author: JerryRigEverything
description: This is our FIRST glow in the dark wheelchair! - and it actually turned out surprisingly well. As long as you have a Portable flashlight or portable UV light to charge it up with. Order your own custom rigid wheelchair at www.Notawheelchair.com and come hang out with us on our youtube channel: @notawheelchair
title: We made a GLOW IN THE DARK Wheelchair!
